org.openimaj.image.processing.face.feature.comparison

Class FaceFVComparator<T extends FacialFeature & FeatureVectorProvider<Q>,Q extends FeatureVector>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openimaj.image.processing.face.feature.comparison.FaceFVComparator<T,Q>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of feature
    Q - Type of featurevector
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    FacialFeatureComparator<T>, ReadableBinary, ReadWriteableBinary, WriteableBinary, DistanceComparator<T>

    public class FaceFVComparator<T extends FacialFeature & FeatureVectorProvider<Q>,Q extends FeatureVector>
extends Object
implements FacialFeatureComparator<T>
    A generic FacialFeatureComparator for FacialFeatures that can provide FeatureVectors through the FeatureVectorProvider interface. Any compatible FVComparator can be used to compare features.
    Author:
    Jonathon Hare (jsh2@ecs.soton.ac.uk)
